West Nile virus infection, birds, Madagascar
----------------------------------------------------
Information received on 21 May 2010 from Dr Bibis Armand Lalaonirina,
Directeur des Services Veterinaires, Ministere de l'Elevage,
Antananarivo, Madagascar

Summary
Report type Immediate notification
Start date: 08 Sep 2009
Date of 1st confirmation of the event: 04 Mar 2010
Report date: 21 May 2010
Date submitted to OIE: 21 May 2010
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease: Sub-clinical infection
Causal agent: West Nile Fever virus
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

